{
  "title": "第2周 第6天 — 不规则复数名词 + 复数综合练习",
  "objective": "<strong>学习目标：</strong>掌握乌克兰语中不规则复数名词的变化规则，重点学习幼崽名词的 -ата/-ята 复数模式，以及完全不规则的常用名词（дитина→діти, людина→люди 等）。通过综合练习巩固第2周所有复数知识。",
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "grammar",
      "heading": "回顾：三种性别的复数规则",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "过去四天我们系统学习了阳性、阴性、中性名词的复数变化。来一个总表快速回顾："
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>复数规则总览</h3><table><thead><tr><th>性别</th><th>单数词尾</th><th>复数变化</th><th>例子</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td rowspan=\"4\">阳性</td><td>辅音</td><td>+ <strong>и</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"桌子\">стіл</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">столи</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ь</td><td>-ь → <strong>і</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"学生\">учень</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">учні</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ж/-ч/-ш/-щ</td><td>+ <strong>і</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"刀\">ніж</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">ножі</span></td></tr><tr><td>飘忽元音</td><td>元音脱落 + <strong>и</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"家\">дім</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">доми</span></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"4\">阴性</td><td>-а</td><td>-а → <strong>и</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"盘子\">тарілка</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">тарілки</span></td></tr><tr><td>-я</td><td>-я → <strong>і</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"裙子\">сукня</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">сукні</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ь</td><td>-ь → <strong>і</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"夜晚\">ніч</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">ночі</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ість</td><td>-ість → <strong>ості</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"喜悦\">радість</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">радості</span></td></tr><tr><td rowspan=\"4\">中性</td><td>-о</td><td>-о → <strong>а</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"扶手椅\">крісло</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">крісла</span></td></tr><tr><td>-е</td><td>-е → <strong>я</strong></td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"田野\">поле</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">поля</span></td></tr><tr><td>-ння/-ття</td><td>不变</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">запитання</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">запитання</span></td></tr><tr><td>外来词</td><td>不变</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"大衣\">пальто</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"大衣\">пальто</span></td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>复习口诀：</strong><br>阳性加 <strong>и/і</strong>，阴性 а→и / я→і，<br>中性 о→а / е→я，ння/ття 和外来词不变！"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "grammar",
      "heading": "1. 语法讲解：不规则复数名词",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "p",
          "html": "大部分乌克兰语名词都遵循上面的规则变复数，但有少数常用名词的复数形式是<strong>不规则的</strong>，需要单独记忆。今天我们按类型逐一学习。"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>A. 完全不规则（词干大变）</h3><p>这些名词的复数形式与单数差别很大，只能死记硬背：</p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>中文</th><th>复数</th><th>变化说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"孩子\">дитина</span></td><td>孩子</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">діти</span></td><td>完全变干，词根大变</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"人\">людина</span></td><td>人</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">люди</span></td><td>完全变干，词根大变</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"名字\">ім'я</span></td><td>名字</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">імена</span></td><td>加 -ена</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"眼睛\">око</span></td><td>眼睛</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">очі</span></td><td>词干变化 к→ч，词尾变 і</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"耳朵\">вухо</span></td><td>耳朵</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">вуха</span></td><td>看似规则（-о→-а），但归为特殊记忆</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>记忆技巧：</strong><br><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"孩子\">дитина</span>（孩子）→ <span class=\"uk-word\">діти</span>（孩子们）—— 想象一群 <strong>di-ti</strong>（弟弟）在玩耍<br><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"人\">людина</span>（人）→ <span class=\"uk-word\">люди</span>（人们）—— 很像英文 \"people\"，单复数也是不同词<br><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"眼睛\">око</span>（眼睛）→ <span class=\"uk-word\">очі</span>（眼睛们）—— к 变成了 ч，就像眼睛「眨」了一下变了样"
        },
        {
          "type": "note",
          "html": "<strong>注意：</strong><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"孩子\">дитина</span> 和 <span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"人\">людина</span> 是第1周已学的词汇，但当时我们只学了它们的单数形式和性别（都是阴性 -а 结尾）。今天我们补充它们的不规则复数。<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"名字\">ім'я</span> 也是第1周学过的（中性特殊词 -м'я 类）。"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>B. 幼崽名词（-а/-я → -ата/-ята）</h3><p>这是乌克兰语的一大特色！<strong>所有动物幼崽</strong>的名词，单数以 <strong>-а</strong> 或 <strong>-я</strong> 结尾，复数统一变为 <strong>-ата</strong> 或 <strong>-ята</strong>。</p><p><strong>变化规则：</strong></p><ul><li>单数以 <strong>-а</strong> 结尾 → 复数去掉 -а，加 <strong>-ата</strong></li><li>单数以 <strong>-я</strong> 结尾 → 复数去掉 -я，加 <strong>-ята</strong></li></ul><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>中文</th><th>复数</th><th>规律</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小鸡\">курча</span></td><td>小鸡</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">курчата</span></td><td>-а → -ата</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小马\">лоша</span></td><td>小马驹</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">лошата</span></td><td>-а → -ата</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小牛\">теля</span></td><td>小牛</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">телята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\">щеня</span></td><td>小狗</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">щенята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小猫\">кошеня</span></td><td>小猫</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">кошенята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小山羊\">козеня</span></td><td>小山羊</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">козенята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小猪\">порося</span></td><td>小猪</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">поросята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小鸭\">каченя</span></td><td>小鸭</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">каченята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"婴儿\">маля</span></td><td>宝宝/幼仔</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">малята</span></td><td>-я → -ята</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>记忆技巧：</strong>看到动物幼崽，就想到 <strong>-ата/-ята</strong>！<br>可以这样记：幼崽们总是成群结队（-ата/-ята 听起来就像一群小动物叽叽喳喳的声音）。<br><br><strong>快速判断法：</strong>如果一个词指的是「小XX」（小鸡、小猫、小狗……），它的复数几乎一定是 -ата/-ята。"
        },
        {
          "type": "error-warn",
          "html": "<strong>易错提醒：</strong><br>幼崽名词虽然单数以 -а/-я 结尾（看起来像阴性），但它们实际上是<strong>中性</strong>名词！<br>例如：<span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"小牛\">теля</span>（小牛）是<strong>中性</strong>，不是阴性。<br>代词用 <span class=\"uk-word\">воно</span>，不用 <span class=\"uk-word\">вона</span>！<br>记住：幼崽名词 = 中性 + 不规则复数 -ата/-ята"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>C. 辅音交替（前几天已学）</h3><p>这些词在变复数时，词干末尾的辅音会发生变化。我们在前几天已经见过：</p><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>中文</th><th>复数</th><th>辅音变化</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"朋友\">друг</span></td><td>朋友</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">друзі</span></td><td>г → з</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"刀\">ніж</span></td><td>刀</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">ножі</span></td><td>і → о（飘忽元音）+ 加 і</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"年\">рік</span></td><td>年</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">роки</span></td><td>і → о（飘忽元音）</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>D. 少数无复数或复数罕用的名词</h3><p>有些名词通常只以单数形式使用，没有复数或复数极少见：</p><ul><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"牛奶\">молоко</span>（牛奶）— 不可数，没有复数</li><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"啤酒\">пиво</span>（啤酒）— 可说 <span class=\"uk-word\">пива</span>（复数），但罕用</li><li><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"头发\">волосся</span>（头发）— 集合名词，本身就表示复数概念</li><li><span class=\"uk-word\">листя</span>（树叶）— 集合名词，本身就表示复数概念</li></ul>"
        },
        {
          "type": "grammar-box",
          "html": "<h3>E. 其他需要注意的复数形式</h3><table><thead><tr><th>单数</th><th>中文</th><th>复数</th><th>说明</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"羽毛\">перо</span></td><td>羽毛</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">пера</span></td><td>按中性 -о→-а 规则（也有 <span class=\"uk-word\">пір'я</span> 的集合形式）</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"肩膀\">плече</span></td><td>肩膀</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">плечі</span></td><td>-е → -і（特殊变化）</td></tr><tr><td><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"膝盖\">коліно</span></td><td>膝盖</td><td><span class=\"uk-word\">коліна</span></td><td>按中性 -о→-а 规则</td></tr></tbody></table>"
        },
        {
          "type": "tip",
          "html": "<strong>-м'я 类词的复数模式：</strong><br><span class=\"uk-word\" data-def=\"名字\">ім'я</span> → <span class=\"uk-word\">імена</span><br>规律：去掉 -'я，加 -ена。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
